entry.title: Russian Strike on Ukraine Sent Warhead Through Polish Airspace, Warsaw Says
entry.content: Russia launched a massive missile and drone attack on cities across Ukraine, killing at least 30 people and allegedly sending a warhead through Polish airspace.

entry.title: Israel Expands Operations in Southern Gaza Amid Worsening Humanitarian Crisis
entry.content: Israeli forces expanded their military operations in Khan Younis as a Hamas delegation headed to Cairo to discuss a proposal to end the war.
